Available Tools: track_delivery | get_order_status | contact_driver | rate_order
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "order_id": "string" }
Response Schema: { "order_id": "string", "status": "string", "driver_name": "string", "eta_minutes": number, "location": "string" }
---
Question: Where is my order #FO-8821 right now?
Call: { "func_call": "track_delivery", "order_id": "FO-8821" }
Response: { "order_id": "FO-8821", "status": "preparing", "driver_name": null, "eta_minutes": 25, "location": "Burger Barn Kitchen" }

